cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS, cs.NE 

This paper proposes a new algorithm for federated learning of modern neural network architectures, such as convolutional neural networks (CNNs) and LSTMs. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also discusses the reduction of communication burden, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
